casebody.data:
Bennie MACK, petitioner,
v.
D. DREW, Individually and in Her Official Capacity as Warden for the Federal Correctional Institute at Bennettsville, South Carolina, et al. No. 13-7677. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 27, 2014. Case below, 520 Fed.Appx. 222 .

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.
